<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 161</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Rights and Health</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic concepts of human rights; historical development of human rights; the Universal Declaration of human rights, human rights and related regulations at the national and international levels; the different groups of society and different environments in terms of the situation of human rights, human rights, development and social relations of inequality; health as a human right.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422298&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 162</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Career Planning</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">27.02.2026</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Career planning is, of course, in the framework of the draft created by the Office of the presidential human resources, videos and activities for each week prepared with academics, industry professionals, civil society organizations and international organizations to be invited by a guest, it is suggested that Trainers be processed. Supporting activities to be included in the course are designed to inform students about the methods and tools used in professional applications and to gain the ability to use them in the most effective way and are supported by practical activities. Career centers will follow the course in practice with activities that provide experience opportunities to support students to develop their skills. The proposed program on the structure and content of the course is presented below. The program in question may vary according to the characteristics of universities and departments where students who will take the course are registered.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422224&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 163</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Technology Addiction</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Within the scope of this course, human interaction with information technologies will be discussed with a developmental perspective. At the end of the course, it is aimed that the students have a theoretical knowledge to discuss the positive and negative aspects of information technology that affect human development, and to define the concept of technology addiction.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422247&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
