<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course;
Testing the entrepreneurship feature, How to find a business idea? Concept of responsible entrepreneurship and sharing of experience with business idea development and creativity exercises.
Concept of responsible entrepreneurship and sharing of experience with business idea development and creativity exercises.
