<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 204</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Power and Inequality</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course will analyze main theories of social stratification and social inequality. It will also focus on global stratification, as well as racial and gender inequalities.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422378&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 208</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Thought</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Presenting examples from the history of human thought/philosophy starting from the Ancient Greek Thought extending to 20th century Phenomenology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422382&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 209</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Musics of The World’s Cultures</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction of world music cultures and examination of musical traditions.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422383&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 210</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Cultural Memory and Photographs</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In recent days memory has become one of the mostly debated issues in social sciences and everyday life. Society and people have become more interested in the past. There are movies, television series and books that are trying to create a connection between the past and present. On the other side photographs are the most important companions in our lives from the day we were born. In this cultural context family photographs became a carrier of cultural memory. This lecture is going to be an introduction to cultural memory and photograph within an interdisciplinary perspective. Both of the topics will be introduced independently and their relation will be discussed critically with the questions and topics such as; how and why we remember?, why we forget?, nostalgic remembering, what a photograph record, ‘reading’ reflections of a photograph.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422384&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 211</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Understanding Everday Life Practices of Turkey</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Everyone of us has daily practices in our lifes such as reading
newspapers, watching tv shows, walking through the city or
going to malls. During the semester we are going to understand
and discuss the meaning of our habits. Why do we have daily
routines? Are we choosing our daily habits? How does the
culture of everyday life in Turkey change? We are going to
discuss such questions within the semester with the help of
selected articles, visual materials- photographs, advertisementsand
our own daily routines.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422385&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 212</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course For Erasmus II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course is for students who wish to prepare for the University’s Erasmus English Proficiency Exam and other internationally recognised test such as IELTS, TOEFL . The lesson covers both examination skills and techniques and work on improving all aspects of the students’ English: speaking, listening, reading, writing, grammar, pronunciation and vocabulary.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422386&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course For Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">B2 Level English</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422387&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History Of Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In class, film viewing will consist primarily of clips, shorts, and portions of documentaries about the history of film. In addition, up to fourteen out-of-class viewings may be assigned as required. All viewings should be approached as PRIMARY TEXTS, not just entertainment. You will be required to think -- seriously and critically -- about what you are seeing. That is, an active (rather than passive) viewing is required. The exams will cover the screenings, the lectures and discussions, and the readings.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422259&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 218</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Gender And Literature</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course is designed to help you gain insight about different literary genres and writers from diverse backgrounds who examine issues of gender and its interplay with race, class, sexuality, and nationality. Moreover you will determine how successful these texts are in articulating a literature of feminism, gender roles and what the future holds for such praxis by means of liberation and empowerment of women.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422260&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 219</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Theory Of Literature And Criticism</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
