<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic Chemistry II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Teaching Methods: Slides, Exercises, Examples and Problems solving.
Content: Structure and geometry of organic molecules, Alkanes, Stereoisomery of organic molecules, Alkenes and Alkynes, Electronic structure of organic compounds, Aromatic compounds, Reactions and mechanism, Alkyl halides, Determination of structures, Alcohols, phenols and ethers, Nomenclature, Aldehydes and ketones, Amines, Carboxylic acids and related derivatives.</Data></Cell>
