<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NUT 128</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutritional Anthropology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Anthropological factors affecting nutrition, origin and basic characteristics of human diet, changes in dietary habits in historical process, differences between eating habits of countries, religions and nutrition.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422390&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NUT 245</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic Microbiology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course is based on learning the relationship between foods and microorganisms, learning the ways of contamination and protection from this contamination. It is a basic course for recognizing microorganisms in general and learning their effects. The course makes a significant contribution to the acquisition of knowledge, skills and competencies required for graduation. The course will be conducted asynchronously and synchronously in a distance education environment. It is aimed to form the basis of theoretical and applied knowledge obtained at the end of the course and to integrate the knowledge with the science of nutrition and dietetics.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422285&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NUT 247</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Food Chemistry and Practices I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Description of food ingredients - chemical structures and various reactions</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422397&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NUT 251</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutritional Biochemistry I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical scope of the course forms the basis of third and fourth year vocational courses and professional practices. The course makes a significant contribution to the acquisition of knowledge, skills and competencies required for graduation.
The course will be conducted with online education method, therefore it will be carried out with teaching methods suitable for online education.
During the course, the metabolism of macronutrients in the body, their advanced functions and their vital importance will be explained in weeks.
Research shows that when students learn the material in an active learning environment, they understand the material at a deeper level and thus retain it for a longer period of time.
In order to facilitate the active learning component of the course, there will be questions that help to think and integrate the learned information and to draw a conceptual map in the brain.
With this method, it will strengthen the learning skills of the students and the permanence of the knowledge in learning the basis of the metabolism of macro and micro nutrients inside and outside the classroom.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422396&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NUT 253</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Principles of Food, Preparation and Cooking Practices I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+2+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Food groups
Starches
Grains
Legumes
Fruit &amp; Vegetables
Seasoning &amp; Flavoring
Food preparation techniques
Cooking methods</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422398&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">NUT 255</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Principles of Nutrition I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
