<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">19.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The theoretical scope of the course forms the basis of vocational courses, professional practices and branches of science supporting this field in the field of nutrition and dietetics in the 3rd and 4th grades. The course contributes to the integration of field and non-field theoretical and applied knowledge, the correct use of scientific literature, access to evidence-based information, and the development of academic writing skills. It contributes to the acquisition of necessary knowledge, skills and competencies for the planning of the nutritional care process and its implementation within the framework of ethical principles.The course will be conducted face to face. In this course, in which student-centered education is used intensively, question-answer, discussion-based learning activities, and discussion of the feedbacks of the given assignments will be included in order to facilitate the active learning component of the course.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422238&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
