<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course contributes to the integration of theoretical and applied knowledge of field and non-field, and to gain the knowledge, skills and competencies required for the planning of the nutritional care process and its implementation within the framework of ethical principles.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422311&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
