<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 172</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Communication Skills and Presentation Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be provided with the knowledge and skills to communicate effectively in family, school, cultural life and business life by getting to know and discover himself. In addition; Listening, talking, introducing yourself, meeting a new person, understanding the other person, expressing your feelings, anger management, sharing, taking responsibility, understanding, in situations such as communication in social life will be created with tips on how to be.To gain mastery of the language rules necessary for literary presentation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422314&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 173</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Law</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Learn the reflections of public and private law, which are covered by health law at the basic level; cases that will cause compensation and acts that will cause criminal sanctions.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422316&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 174</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Environmental Pollution and Climate Change</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be provided with the knowledge and skills to communicate effectively in family, school, cultural life and business life by getting to know and discover himself. In addition; Listening, talking, introducing yourself, meeting a new person, understanding the other person, expressing your feelings, anger management, sharing, taking responsibility, understanding, in situations such as communication in social life will be created with tips on how to be.To gain mastery of the language rules necessary for literary presentation</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422239&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 175</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Creativity and Art</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Recognize the concept of creativity. Classify the branches of art. Learn the method of drama. Develop creative thinking skills. Use creative techniques. Apply creative and artistic activities in social and professional life. Evaluate the obstacles in front of creativity.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422334&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 176</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Music, Individual and Society</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Müzikal kavramları tanır. Müzik tarihi dönemlerini öğrenir. Müzik, birey ve toplum ilişkisini kavrar. Müziğe sosyolojik bakış açısı geliştirir. Sosyal yaşamda temel müzik bilgisini kullanır. Müzik, birey ve toplum ilişkisini değerlendirir. Bir sanat dalı olan müzik üzerine interdisipliner yaklaşımla tartışır.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422243&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Nutrition and Dietetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6107</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 178</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Modern Scientific Research Methods</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To be able to understand the basic principles and processes in the realization of research, To learn different research methods, To be able to analyze data and develop solutions, and to interpret the results obtained with the help of software.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=422242&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
