<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Can comment on how gender roles are handled in genres of Western literature such as novels, stories, plays, essays and poetry.</Data></Cell>
