<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Defines the conditions under which the composition of foods deteriorate and how the appropriate consumption should be, as cause and effect.</Data></Cell>
