<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">She/he is able to explain the acute and chronic diseases commonly seen in adults, the etiology, symptoms, complications and treatment methods of these diseases.</Data></Cell>
