<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">She/he is able to calculate the patient&apos;s energy, macronutrient and micronutrient requirements by considering age, gender, physical activity status, food consumption, anthropometric measurements, biochemical and clinical data of adult patients.</Data></Cell>
