<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Reading Skill-At the end of this course, students will be able to
• read for/understand specific information, main ideas, gist and opinions
• Use pre-reading skills to activate schemata and predict content of advanced texts
• identify the common types of support in arguments, their relevance and irrelevance, common argument flaws, opposing points of views and refutations
• expand targeted vocabulary</Data></Cell>
