<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The Horror Film</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">10</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Investigating the Serial Killer (1990’s)
Reading: Wells, The Horror Genre, Chapter 3 (pgs. 89-101; 105-112)
Film: The Silence of the Lambs (Jonathan Demme, 1991)</Data></Cell>
